Description: From the publisher: "The campus culture festival is coming up for the students of Class 2-A." That means starting an all-girl band, despite the keyboardist being a boy.
Title: NEON GENESIS EVANGELION, VOL. 11
Author: Osamu Takahashi

Description: Yuma Tsukumo will stop at nothing to become the Duel Masters champion, but as a rank amateur, the odds are stacked against him. Luckily, he has a mysterious spirit named Astral to help him.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 1
Author: Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 14
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work — as a boy — for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 18
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Lydia Carlton, who is interested in fairy lore, meets Edgar, who is seeking a mystical sword that may be his birthright.
Title: THE EARL AND THE FAIRY, VOL. 2
Author: Ayuko

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 40
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Princess Nakaba and Prince Caesar are married to keep peace between warring countries. Will they learn to love each other?
Title: DAWN OF THE ARCANA, VOL. 4
Author: Rei Toma

Description: This series is about Arata and his cross-dressing adventures in a world where humans and gods live side by side.
Title: ARATA: THE LEGEND, VOL. 10
Author: Yuu Watase

Description: Jiro, a werewolf, falls for Kaya, a cafe owner who also guards a haunted cemetery. This is their love story.
Title: THREE WOLVES MOUNTAIN, VOL. 1
Author: Bohra Naouo

Description: Chihiro finds his calling when Kumazawa, a handsome vet, takes care of his kitten. He gets to work at the clinic but only if he becomes Kumazawa’s live-in housekeeper. This is their love story.
Title: HONEY DARLING, VOL. 1
Author: Norikazu Akira
